snippet.title: Macbat 64 - Feed your classic 3D platformer fix (for fans of Super Mario 64, Banjo Kazooie)
snippet.description:
Get on itch.io https://siactro.itch.io/macbat64 Do you miss the days of 3D character platformers? Were the late 90s your favorite time for games? If so, check out Macbat in this wacky nostalgia trip.

#itchio #indiegames
